ce:section.ce:para:
The BA gene sequence of B. gladioli was obtained from the GenBank database. The specific primers were designed using the NUPACK software (
                           http://www.nupack.org/
                        ), and the DINAMelt Web Server (
                           http://unafold.rna.albany.edu/?q=DINAMelt
                        ). The primers were screened for primer specificity and cross-reactivity using local nucleotide alignment tool (
                           http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/blast
                        ). The 5′ ends of primers SEA-F and SEA-R were modified with biotin and -COOH, respectively，and were synthesized by Sangon Biotech (Shanghai, China) and purified by High Performance Liquid Chromatography.
